=板橋雜記 Diverse Records from the Wooden Bridge=
work by [[余懷]] in 3 juan. Describes the pleasure quarters in Nanjing an the end of the Ming dynasty.
==Literature==
===Monographs===
* [[Howard S. Levy]]: A Feast of Mist and Flowers: The Gay Quarters of Nanking at the End of the Ming. Yokohama, 1966
